# G7 Subject Allowlist
# Modules listed here have event subject patterns that look like double-prefix
# but are intentional by design. Each entry documents why.
#
# Format: module_name  # reason
#
# The publisher constructs subjects as: module.events.{event_type}
# If event_type constants already start with "module.", the final subject
# becomes module.events.module.action — which is flagged by G7 as a
# double-prefix. Modules listed here have reviewed and accepted this pattern.

ar  # ar.events.ar.* is intentional — event_type constants use ar. prefix for cross-module routing clarity
